\brief The low 7 bits of a triangle material index.
These low bits are concatenated with the high bits from NxHeightFieldShapeDesc::materialIndexHighBits, to produce an index into the scene's material array. This index determines the material of the upper of the quad's two triangles (i.e. the quad whose upper-left corner is this sample, see the Guide for illustrations).
@see NxHeightFieldShapeDesc materialIndex0

\brief The low 7 bits of a triangle material index.
These low bits are concatenated with the high bits from NxHeightFieldShapeDesc::materialIndexHighBits, to produce an index into the scene's material array. This index determines the material of the lower of the quad's two triangles (i.e. the quad whose upper-left corner is this sample, see the Guide for illustrations).
@see NxHeightFieldShapeDesc materialIndex1

	\brief The height of the heightfield sample

	This value is scaled by NxHeightFieldShapeDesc::heightScale.

	@see NxHeightFieldShapeDesc

